> Hi,
>
> In addition to careful balancing and CCing the combustion chambers, what
> else would contribute to smoothness and quietness of a running VW engine.
>

Hydraulic lifters will definitely help, but well adjusted solids can be
quiet too. Some other things:

Electronic ignition.
Solid exhaust.
Good motor mounts.
Proper valve adjustment.
Complete stock intake or well designed aftermarket with clean air filters.




